  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Making Your Decision</h2>
    
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Your analytics requirements depend on your scale and goals:
    </p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 space-y-3 mb-4">
      <li><strong>For new course creators:</strong> Basic progress reports and enrollment tracking (available on all plans) are sufficient. Focus on creating content before optimizing based on data.</li>
      
      <li><strong>For growing learning businesses:</strong> Engagement dashboards (Thinkific Grow+, Kajabi, Teachable) reveal optimization opportunities. Look for video analytics and cohort analysis.</li>
      
      <li><strong>For academies and bootcamps:</strong> Student Performance Dashboards and role-based access let instructors support students without exposing sensitive business data.</li>
      
      <li><strong>For certification programs:</strong> SCORM reporting is essential for compliance documentation. Thinkific Plus or enterprise platforms provide this.</li>
      
      <li><strong>For enterprise training:</strong> Predictive analytics and extensive API access (Docebo, Absorb) support integration with existing business systems.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

